videos.description: Nickk Popovic gets the Eagles out early with a tough jumper over the Seminoles.
videos.headline: BC's Popovic knocks down early jumper

videos.description: Steffon Mitchell gets left open for a 3-pointer that gives Boston College a 10-point lead.
videos.headline: Mitchell 3-pointer puts Eagles up 10

videos.description: Jerome Robinson drives and fires a pass to Ky Bowman who knocks down the Eagles 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Robinson zips pass to Bowman 3-pointer

videos.description: Jordan Chatman takes advantage of the hustle from Steffon Mitchell and knocks down a big 3-pointer for the Eagles.
videos.headline: Chatman puts BC up 19 with 3-pointer

videos.description: Jerome Robinson gets the give-and-go from Nik Popovic and lifts in the basket before hitting the floor.
videos.headline: Robinson hits tough layup for Eagles

videos.description: FSU's CJ Walker drives and has to toss up a shot while falling back that goes in as he draws a foul.
videos.headline: Walker draws the foul on tough shot

videos.description: BC's Nik Popovic rolls off a screen and is left alone by 3 defenders for the open two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Popovic left open for big dunk

videos.description: Jerome Robinson draws a foul as he drains a jumper from the corner for Boston College.
videos.headline: Robinson hits step-back and-1
